text: Cass County is the name of nine counties in the United States; eight of which are named for Michigan governor, senator and presidential candidate Lewis Cass: *Cass County, Illinois *Cass County, Indiana *Cass County, Iowa *Cass County, Michigan *Cass County, Minnesota *Cass County, Missouri *Cass County, Nebraska *Cass County, North Dakota (named for George Washington Cass) *Cass County, Texas ;Other *Bartow County, Georgia was formerly called Cass County *Cass County (album), an album by Don Henley
title: Cass County
